    java.lang.Cloneable

    @Preamble(description="Options to use when listing campaign device metadatas.")
public class CampaignDeviceMetadataListOptions
extends ListOptions
    Options to use when listing campaign device metadatas.

    Note:

    • Filters:

      The list can be filtered server-side on some of the fields of a campaign device metadata.

      The following filters are currently supported:

      Server-side filters
      Field Tag Filters
      not equal to equal to greater than less than like in not in
